'''Hello Games Ltd'''是英国一家游戏开发商和发行商，总部设在英国吉尔福德，因开发制作了《[[无人深空|无人深空]]》（No Man's Sky）而知名。

== 简介 ==
Hello Games由其他电子游戏公司（如[[Criterion_Games|Criterion Games]]、[[艺电|艺电]]和[[Kuju_Entertainment|Kuju Entertainment]]）的前雇员于2008年2月成立。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.facebook.com/HelloGames/about/?tab=page_info | title = About Hello Games | website = [[Facebook|Facebook]] | accessdate = 2016-08-17 | archive-date = 2019-02-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190216135240/https://www.facebook.com/HelloGames/about/?tab=page_info | dead-url = no }}</ref>

在2010年Develop大奖中，该工作室获得两个奖项：最佳新工作室和最佳微型工作室。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2010/jul/15/develop-games-awards-2010 | title = Develop Awards - Heavy Rain, Angry Birds, Arkham amongst winners | last = Howson | first = Greg | date = 2010-07-15 | website = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | publisher = [[Guardian_News_and_Media|Guardian News and Media]] | accessdate = 2016-08-17 | archive-date = 2016-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160809080655/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2010/jul/15/develop-games-awards-2010 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/hello-games-wins-2-awards | title = Hello Games wins 2 awards | last = Elliott | first = Phil | date = 2010-07-15 | website = [[GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]] | publisher = [[Gamer_Network|Gamer Network]] | accessdate = 2016-08-17 | archive-date = 2016-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160809080658/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/hello-games-wins-2-awards | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2010年9月，他们被《[[衛報|衛報]]》100个在创立时间在12个月内的最具创新性和创造性的公司之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/tech-media-invest-100/top-100-technology-innovators |title=Tech media invest 100 |date=2010-09-13 |website=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |publisher=[[Guardian_News_and_Media|Guardian News and Media]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129192730/http://www.theguardian.com/tech-media-invest-100/top-100-technology-innovators |archivedate=2014-11-29 |accessdate=2016-08-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

在2011年的科隆游戏展新闻发布会上，他们公布第二款游戏：《Joe Danger 2: The Movie》。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.engadget.com/2011/08/12/joe-danger-the-movie-is-hello-games-next-stunt/ | title = Joe Danger: The Movie is Hello Games' next stunt | last = Fletcher | first = JC | date = 2011-08-12 | website = [[Engadget|Engadget]] | publisher = [[AOL_Tech|AOL Tech]] | accessdate = 2016-08-17 | archive-date = 2016-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160818033246/https://www.engadget.com/2011/08/12/joe-danger-the-movie-is-hello-games-next-stunt/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

在VGX 2013中，Hello Games宣布开发一个新的科幻冒险游戏《无人深空》。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.kotaku.com.au/2013/12/wow-no-mans-sky-just-stole-the-show-at-the-vgx/ | title = Wow. No Man's Sky Just Stole The Show At The VGX | last = Good | first = Owen | date = 2013-12-08 | website = [[Kotaku_Australia|Kotaku Australia]] | publisher = [[Allure_Media|Allure Media]] | accessdate = 2016-08-17 | archive-date = 2016-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160809080710/http://www.kotaku.com.au/2013/12/wow-no-mans-sky-just-stole-the-show-at-the-vgx/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

2013年12月24日，工作室的办公室被附近的河流爆发的洪水淹没 ，其中大部分在游戏开发中使用的硬件被摧毁。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/12/26/hello-games-hit-by-flood | title = Hello Games Hit By Flood | last = Nix | first = Marc | date = 2013-12-26 | website = [[IGN|IGN]] | publisher = [[IGN_Entertainment|IGN Entertainment]] | accessdate = 2016-08-17 | archive-date = 2016-08-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160821161536/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/12/26/hello-games-hit-by-flood | dead-url = no }}</ref>

《无人深空》原定在2016年6月发布，但在一个月前，穆雷宣布游戏延迟发布，需要时间修正，并会在两个月后的8月推出。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://blog.us.playstation.com/2016/05/27/no-mans-sky-coming-to-ps4-in-august/ | title = No Man's Sky Coming to PS4 in August | last = Murray | first = Sean | date = 2016-05-27 | website = [[PlayStation_Blog|PlayStation Blog]] | publisher = [[Sony_Interactive_Entertainment|Sony Interactive Entertainment]] | accessdate = 2016-08-17 | archive-date = 2016-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160809080712/http://blog.us.playstation.com/2016/05/27/no-mans-sky-coming-to-ps4-in-august/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

Hello Games因在《无人深空》中的欺骗行为而饱受批评。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-anatomy-of-hype-how-no-mans-sky-became-the-best-and-worst-game-ever/ | title=The anatomy of hype: how No Man's Sky became the best and worst game ever | last=Wilde | first=Tyler | date=2016-08-15 | publisher=PC Gamer | accessdate=2016-08-31 | archive-date=2016-09-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160902023621/http://www.pcgamer.com/the-anatomy-of-hype-how-no-mans-sky-became-the-best-and-worst-game-ever/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

